BUILD
  Construct ships, land units, or planes in a sector.

SYNTAX
  build s <sects> <type#> [count]   ship
  build l <sects> <type#> [count]   land unit
  build p <sects> <type#> [count]   plane
  buil  s|l|p <sects> <type#> [count]

DESCRIPTION
  Builds a new unit in a suitable sector.  Only one at a time for
  players; deities can specify a count.

  SHIPS — must be built in a harbor (type 'h') at >=60% efficiency.
    Materials required (at 20% efficiency): ~20% of full cost in LCM
    and HCM.  The ship appears at 20% efficiency and builds toward
    100% over updates as long as it has crew and materials.
    Ship types: use 'show s b' to see all types and costs.

  LAND UNITS — can be built in any owned sector.
    Require LCM and HCM proportional to type.
    Use 'show l b' to see all types and costs.

  PLANES — must be built in an airfield (type '*') at >=60% eff.
    Require LCM, HCM, and sometimes oil.
    Use 'show p b' to see all types and costs.

  All builds require 'avail' workforce in the sector (shown in
  census).  Materials are deducted from the sector at build time.

EXAMPLE
  build s 6,0 0 1           build 1 fishing boat (type 0) at 6,0
  build s 6,0 6 1           build 1 frigate (type 6) at 6,0
  build l 0,0 0 1           build 1 land unit (type 0) at capital
  show s b                  list all ship types and requirements

SEE ALSO
  show  ship  census  resource  designate  sector-types  scrap  scuttle
